➜实用英语：关于夏天的英文知识
http://www.sohu.com/a/414231076_100171577	22399
<p>虽然立秋了，但是苏州的天气还是热的火辣辣的，所以这些关于夏天的英文小知识快储备起来！</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200821/7b2c50b0510d4255b246ec2f6e923f2c.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>炎热的夏天</strong></p>
<p>1. I think I was affected by the heat.</p>
<p>我觉得我被炎热的天气影响了。</p>
<p>2. The temperature went up to 36 degrees.</p>
<p>气温升到了36度。</p>
<p>3. I was soaked from sweat.</p>
<p>我被汗水湿透了。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200821/5e6b02ebb44847dfb2c99ae76c148e65.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>防暑</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
