<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p>1. Would you turn the fan on?</p>
<p>你能把电扇打开嘛？</p>
<p>2. Can you turn the air conditioner down a little bit?</p>
<p>你能把空调关小一点嘛？</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200821/a60660b284ab4c3cbc5c1d26af5c7583.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>夏季害虫</strong></p>
<p>1. I spent all night killing mosquitoes.</p>
<p>我整晚都在打蚊子。</p>
<p>2. I had 10 bug bites on my left leg.</p>
<p>我左腿上有10个虫子包。</p>
<p>3. What about putting up a mosquito net?</p>
<p>挂蚊帐怎么样？</p>
<p>4. I couldn’t sleep at all because of the mosquitoes.</p>
<p>因为蚊子我完全无法入睡。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200821/633c23f753b5498fb0ebc3b559dae157.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p><strong>梅雨</strong></p>
<p>1. Since it’s the rainy season, I feel sticky.</p>
<p>因为是雨季，所以我觉得黏黏的。</p>
<p>2. Everything seems to be damp in the rainy season.</p>
<p>雨季里每样东西看上去都很潮湿。</p>